<img src="/content/dam/pan/en_US/images/privacy/xnotification-of-changes.png.pagespeed.ic.Qvf93YEnLk.png">
<h2>Notification of Changes</h2>
<p>This privacy statement may be changed or updated from time to time. We will post the date of the changes at the beginning of this statement. Please check this privacy statement from time to time to make sure that you are aware of our current privacy practices.</p>
</section>
